@TITLE "Welcome"
@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}- Laplace Manual --------------------------------------------------- Welcome -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}

@REM KEY 0 0 "" "Welcome"
   Welcome to Laplace V0.13  (beta version), a program  by P!\K.  This  manual
describes the installation and usage of  the Laplace program. The last  update
was on 29.9.1998.

   Laplace is SHAREWARE!! Look at @{"Registration" LINK "Introduction.guide/Registration"} or @{"Copyright" LINK "Introduction.guide/Copyright"} for more  informa-
tion.

   A brand new feature is the asynchron calculation. While Laplace is doing  a
calculation, you  can continue  editing.  You can  abort the  calculation,  by
pressing @{B}ctrl c@{UB} or the @{B}abort@{UB} button. This feature is still quite experimental.
If you have problems, you  can disable it (@{I}Preferences/Misc/asyncron  calcula-@{UI}
@{I}tion @{UI}). But don't forget a (detailed, if possible) bug-report...

